Aleksandra Grigoryeva (née Deverinskaya; Russian: Александра Деверинская-Григорьева; amụrụ na 19 Machị n'afọ 1960) bụ onye Russia bụbu onye na-eme egwuregwu na-agba ọsọ. Ọ bụ onye nwetara ihe nrite ọla edo na 1985 Summer Universiade, na-aghọ onye mmeri mbụ nke ụmụ nwanyị na-aga ije na ihe omume ahụ. Ọ nọchitere anya Soviet Union na 1986 European Athletics Championships.

Ọ bụ onye nwetara ihe nrite ugboro abụọ na IAAF World Race Walking Cup, na-ewere ọlaọcha na 1981 ma soro onye otu ya Olga Krishtop kerịta ọla nchara na 1985. Ọ bụkwa onye nwetara ọla nchara na 1986 Goodwill Games. O meriri na Soviet Athletics Championships na afọ 1981, na-ewere aha 5000m ije.
Ọ bụ onye na-agba ọsọ ọsọ ọsọ 5000 mita, ebe o setịpụrụ oge nke 22:30.0 nkeji na Moscow na 2 Mee n'afo 1982.
